If you haven’t felt the touch of pure-grade badger hair, your life is a song half-sung. These woodland whiskers will massage your own into ultrasoft submission, rendering them ripe and ready for your blade to cut. With an ergonomic handle—made for comfort and endurance—this time-honored staple is truly a cut above.

After dipping the brush in warm water, remove the excess droplets by gently smoothing the bristles from the handle-down. Create a small divot in the center of the bristles and add a tiny dollop of shaving cream. Lather up your face using small circular motions, and shave as usual. After you’ve finished, rinse and hang the brush bristles-down (if possible), allowing gravity to help it dry.
